      "content": "i know about the hotlines, i've tried them. they just give you the same scripts. they don't understand what it's like to have your own body feel like a torture chamber every single second. it feels less like \"distress\" and more like there's just no logical reason to keep going through this. it feels like death would just be a mercy at this point. isn't there any mercy in just letting the pain stop?",
